OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781531287
OL,3,CEsso fined #1 million after 'partial
OL,4,Ccollapse' caused 33 hour long gas leak
OL,6,FEsso has been fined #1 million by the
OL,7,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE),
OL,8,Fafter a tower at its Fawley Refinery
OL,9,FSite partially collapsed.
OL,11,FThe incident happened on 8 November
OL,12,F2022, and led to the release of
OL,13,Fliquefied petroleum gas for 33 hours,
OL,14,Fwith roughly 2,400kg being released
OL,15,Finto the atmosphere.
OL,17,FHSE says workers were in the vicinity
OL,18,Fat the time, and were put at risk of
OL,19,Fserious injuries from falling debris,
OL,20,Fas well as burns had the gas ignited.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
